<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">匿名用户</h3></div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="348">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-ya-ya-28" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-ya-ya-28" class="zg-link" title="张雅雅">张雅雅</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$bing-zi-33-1" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/bing-zi-33-1" class="zg-link" title="饼子">饼子</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$phaladius" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/phaladius" class="zg-link" title="道鱼酱">道鱼酱</a></span>
